name: Wendy Ellin

jv_history.source_quote: I was honored to be featured in this Q&A series at Costco that is highlighting our IT team members. In lieu of singing advertising jingles, you’ll find Ellin Sidell busy

what_you_do: Wendy Ellin is a speaker and author who helps people uncover the hidden stress caused by lack of organizational systems, and how to implement systems to increase productivity, performance, and profitability.
social_proof: Wendy Ellin is a #1 bestselling author and has been featured in media outlets such as The Wall Street Journal, NPR, NBC TV, and more.
signature_programs: Wendy Ellin's book "Working From Home... How's That Working For You?" is an Amazon #1 bestseller.
business_focus: Helping busy professionals and business owners eliminate stress and increase productivity, performance, and profitability through organizational systems.
